WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:10.000
[English subtitles are available]

01:31.430 --> 01:34.940
[Road Home]

01:35.289 --> 01:37.840
[Episode 9]

01:38.890 --> 01:39.460
Are you busy?

01:46.140 --> 01:46.900
I'm on leave today.

01:50.430 --> 01:52.020
Is Qin Xiaonan okay?

02:04.030 --> 02:04.580
He said

02:05.180 --> 02:05.820
he misses you.

02:09.460 --> 02:10.500
Great. Let me tell you.

02:10.690 --> 02:11.730
Fishing there is...

02:12.540 --> 02:13.840
Chen. Do you want to go fishing?

02:14.120 --> 02:14.650
Let's go together.

02:15.020 --> 02:15.580
No.

02:16.340 --> 02:17.130
Okay, let's go.

02:17.130 --> 02:17.700
That place...

02:19.060 --> 02:19.380
Wait.

02:20.220 --> 02:20.780
What?

02:21.500 --> 02:22.070
Do you want to go fishing?

02:22.680 --> 02:22.960
Yes.

02:24.030 --> 02:24.450
But

02:24.720 --> 02:25.360
I'm okay if I don't.

02:26.790 --> 02:27.120
Go ahead then.

02:27.810 --> 02:28.450
It's Chinese New Year.

02:29.030 --> 02:29.550
It's rare to be on holiday.

02:30.579 --> 02:31.380
Not at all.

02:32.130 --> 02:33.240
I've been on winter vacation for a long time.

02:34.300 --> 02:35.100
Just do as I say.

02:35.950 --> 02:37.470
Boys should exercise more.

02:39.820 --> 02:40.370
Come on.

02:41.300 --> 02:42.820
Bring him to have a nice dinner after fishing.

02:43.450 --> 02:44.000
No problem.

02:44.100 --> 02:44.780
Leave him to us.

02:45.100 --> 02:45.670
Come back later.

02:45.990 --> 02:46.290
Okay.

02:47.100 --> 02:47.510
Let's go.

04:00.570 --> 04:01.090
Chen.

04:01.700 --> 04:02.930
You've been standing here for half an hour.

04:03.140 --> 04:03.690
Aren't you cold?

04:10.370 --> 04:10.900
I'm here.

04:18.700 --> 04:19.200
Drive in.

04:19.720 --> 04:20.399
Let me take a look at your car.

04:24.220 --> 04:24.620
Come out.

04:25.200 --> 04:25.540
I'll drive.

04:39.040 --> 04:45.220
[Lu Zheng Automobile Repair]

04:47.340 --> 04:47.780
Miss.

04:48.659 --> 04:50.280
Have you gotten your car fixed?

04:51.790 --> 04:53.180
Yes, it's fixed. Thank you.

05:00.380 --> 05:01.060
It's driving a little crooked.

05:01.700 --> 05:02.650
The noise is strong too.

05:07.310 --> 05:07.820
Soda water.

05:10.940 --> 05:11.580
Later, I'll check

05:11.580 --> 05:12.540
your tire pressure

05:13.010 --> 05:14.040
and wheel alignment

05:16.540 --> 05:17.260
before checking the tires.

05:20.060 --> 05:21.100
Did it shake very badly

05:21.180 --> 05:22.140
when you warmed up the car this morning?

05:22.740 --> 05:23.820
Not too bad.

05:26.210 --> 05:27.180
What do you mean?

05:27.860 --> 05:28.740
Didn't you drive this car?

05:30.800 --> 05:32.380
I don't usually drive.

05:32.380 --> 05:33.130
I go on business trips very often.

05:33.600 --> 05:34.790
Is there a problem?

05:36.180 --> 05:37.100
There's a problem with the valve train.

05:38.370 --> 05:39.250
Just drive on the expressway more often

05:39.450 --> 05:40.270
and it'll sort itself out.

05:41.720 --> 05:42.920
You're quite good at lying.

05:44.010 --> 05:44.710
What did I lie to you about?

05:45.940 --> 05:47.270
Last year, someone fooled me

05:47.300 --> 05:48.600
into aligning my tires.

05:48.860 --> 05:50.020
Did they mess up?

05:52.740 --> 05:53.659
It's not that they fooled you.

05:54.920 --> 05:56.490
It's because of your technique.

05:59.060 --> 05:59.580
Alright.

06:00.190 --> 06:01.110
I'll leave it to you.

06:07.140 --> 06:07.780
Where's Qin Xiaonan?

06:09.690 --> 06:10.270
He went fishing.

06:12.780 --> 06:14.130
Didn't he say he missed me?

06:14.410 --> 06:15.160
He still went fishing.

06:16.170 --> 06:17.180
He's just a kid.

06:17.700 --> 06:19.260
He doesn't remember the things he says.

06:20.310 --> 06:21.300
When will he be back?

06:21.300 --> 06:21.860
I brought him

06:21.860 --> 06:22.700
a lot of delicious food.

06:23.500 --> 06:23.930
I don't know.

06:25.360 --> 06:26.230
He should be back quite late.

06:32.740 --> 06:33.500
What is this?

06:36.340 --> 06:36.940
Ring spanner.

06:38.220 --> 06:38.780
What about that one?

06:38.800 --> 06:39.120
That one.

06:41.300 --> 06:42.100
Socket wrench.

06:43.090 --> 06:43.620
What is it for?

06:45.500 --> 06:46.180
It turns

06:46.860 --> 06:47.659
the bolts

06:48.470 --> 06:49.070
on tires.

06:54.050 --> 06:54.480
Go in.

06:55.400 --> 06:56.600
Don't we need to check the car?

06:57.250 --> 06:57.840
We'll do it in the afternoon.

06:58.780 --> 06:59.700
It's too cold in the garage.

07:00.290 --> 07:00.860
It's warm inside.

07:02.060 --> 07:02.340
Okay.

07:07.030 --> 07:11.370
[Finance Room]

07:20.950 --> 07:21.350
Hello?

07:21.660 --> 07:22.500
Your son brought a girl

07:22.500 --> 07:23.260
to the garage.

07:26.750 --> 07:27.660
It's messy because of the kid.

07:28.500 --> 07:29.500
I tried tidying up.

07:30.630 --> 07:32.140
It used to be even messier.

07:46.780 --> 07:47.940
I remember the first time

07:47.940 --> 07:48.980
I came here,

07:49.409 --> 07:50.530
there was a pile of test papers here.

07:52.820 --> 07:54.340
I still get scared when I hear the words

07:54.340 --> 07:55.020
"test paper."

07:55.620 --> 07:56.580
I did too many of them in high school.

07:59.460 --> 08:00.100
Can you understand it?

08:02.060 --> 08:03.030
Of course.

08:03.240 --> 08:04.210
It's such a simple question.

08:08.170 --> 08:09.220
I remember that in our time,

08:09.250 --> 08:09.950
the math papers

08:10.260 --> 08:11.500
were carved and printed

08:11.500 --> 08:12.260
by the teachers themselves.

08:13.020 --> 08:13.740
Every time I finished one,

08:13.740 --> 08:14.920
my hand would have blue smudges on it.

08:15.340 --> 08:16.140
I couldn't even wash them off.

08:17.100 --> 08:17.500
Really?

08:19.060 --> 08:19.900
I bought my test papers

08:20.070 --> 08:21.270
at the school gate.

08:22.740 --> 08:24.240
Our teacher was thrifty.

08:24.540 --> 08:25.540
He carved it all himself.

08:27.060 --> 08:27.860
I remember

08:27.860 --> 08:29.140
my math teacher

08:29.140 --> 08:30.020
was already 60

08:30.020 --> 08:30.910
when he taught me.

08:31.890 --> 08:33.280
I wonder how he's doing now.

08:33.669 --> 08:34.230
Is he doing well?

08:48.520 --> 08:49.530
The first time I saw you

08:50.130 --> 08:51.060
at the gas station,

08:52.410 --> 08:53.090
I didn't dare to approach you.

08:56.500 --> 08:57.580
You still look the same,

09:00.540 --> 09:01.480
but you've suddenly grown up.

09:04.900 --> 09:05.620
The door is open.

09:38.430 --> 09:38.890
Lu—

09:45.020 --> 09:46.060
I...

09:47.130 --> 09:48.490
I came back in a hurry

09:48.520 --> 09:49.980
to see Aunt Gui Xiao.

09:51.780 --> 09:52.580
It's not enough just to have fish.

09:53.340 --> 09:53.940
We need vegetables.

09:56.600 --> 09:57.440
Yes.

09:59.370 --> 09:59.900
Let's go grocery shopping.

10:01.020 --> 10:01.460
Okay.

10:25.140 --> 10:26.670
Hello, are you looking for Lu Chen?

10:28.130 --> 10:28.850
You are?

10:29.800 --> 10:31.080
I'm his classmate.

10:31.720 --> 10:32.610
His ex-classmate.

10:35.580 --> 10:36.480
Auntie, who are you?

10:37.140 --> 10:38.320
I’m Lu Chen’s mother.

10:41.220 --> 10:41.920
Hello, Auntie.

10:42.940 --> 10:43.540
Where is Lu Chen?

10:44.180 --> 10:45.100
He went out to buy groceries.

10:45.100 --> 10:45.780
He'll be back soon.

10:49.120 --> 10:50.460
He left you here alone

10:50.780 --> 10:51.760
to go grocery shopping?

10:54.290 --> 10:55.260
Have a seat.

10:55.570 --> 10:56.600
I'll wait outside.

10:56.660 --> 10:57.380
It's okay.

10:57.400 --> 10:58.040
Sit down.

11:05.460 --> 11:06.380
Why don't you sit down?

11:11.040 --> 11:11.840
What's your name?

11:12.170 --> 11:12.690
Gui Xiao.

11:14.380 --> 11:15.950
"Gui" as in return, "Xiao" as in dawn.

11:20.560 --> 11:21.480
Auntie, let me help you.

11:22.300 --> 11:22.970
It's okay.

11:23.230 --> 11:23.900
You are our guest.

11:24.130 --> 11:24.770
Sit down.

11:34.590 --> 11:35.380
Auntie, I’ll leave you alone.

11:35.380 --> 11:36.770
I need to make a call.

12:04.800 --> 12:05.400
Miss.

12:06.210 --> 12:06.820
Are you cold?

12:07.900 --> 12:08.860
I'm fine. I'm not cold.

12:11.970 --> 12:12.300
Here.

12:12.940 --> 12:13.500
Come side inside.

12:14.800 --> 12:15.710
Will I be a bother?

12:16.320 --> 12:17.060
I was hoping

12:17.060 --> 12:18.340
someone would come talk to me.

12:21.580 --> 12:22.500
Sit there. It's warm.

12:25.750 --> 12:26.320
Do you want some tea?

12:26.610 --> 12:27.530
No, thanks.

12:30.510 --> 12:33.630
Did you meet Lu Chen through car repair?

12:36.380 --> 12:38.140
No, we were classmates.

12:38.860 --> 12:39.610
Middle school classmates.

12:46.350 --> 12:47.160
Lu Chen, you're here?

12:47.630 --> 12:48.910
You bought so many vegetables.

12:49.210 --> 12:50.450
Do you have guests over?

12:52.150 --> 12:52.690
Give me a big one.

12:52.950 --> 12:53.300
Okay.

12:56.330 --> 12:57.140
Give me half a catty

12:57.480 --> 12:58.350
of prawns.

12:59.340 --> 13:00.140
Prawns are expensive

13:00.140 --> 13:01.160
these days.

13:01.650 --> 13:02.780
It's going to be Chinese New Year soon.

13:03.120 --> 13:04.260
It's expensive for me to get them too.

13:04.260 --> 13:05.180
The price has gone up.

13:05.870 --> 13:06.670
I have no choice.

13:07.100 --> 13:08.290
-It’s okay, go ahead. -I'm not scamming you.

13:08.550 --> 13:09.020
Okay.

13:15.990 --> 13:16.800
Give me another one.

13:17.350 --> 13:17.870
Pick the best one.

13:23.330 --> 13:23.810
Auntie.

13:25.320 --> 13:25.860
You're leaving?

13:27.860 --> 13:29.550
You're leaving after changing his sheets?

13:30.050 --> 13:31.820
He doesn't want me around.

13:37.500 --> 13:38.640
If it's convenient for you,

13:39.760 --> 13:40.850
come with him to have a meal

13:40.880 --> 13:41.760
at my house.

13:43.090 --> 13:44.220
Let that kid

13:44.570 --> 13:45.410
come too.

13:48.500 --> 13:49.640
I'll let him know when he comes back.

13:51.540 --> 13:52.060
See you.

13:52.930 --> 13:53.450
Take care.

14:33.390 --> 14:34.110
Why did you come out?

14:37.290 --> 14:38.760
Your mother came just now.

14:39.900 --> 14:41.290
She seemed a little unhappy.

14:41.320 --> 14:42.450
I was afraid I might say something wrong,

14:42.830 --> 14:43.600
so I came out for a while.

14:45.960 --> 14:46.790
Did she bully you?

14:48.340 --> 14:48.820
No.

14:50.140 --> 14:51.340
Your mother is nice.

14:52.300 --> 14:53.540
She even asked Qin Xiaonan and me

14:53.900 --> 14:54.820
to go eat at your house.

14:56.940 --> 14:58.190
Are we going?

15:00.060 --> 15:00.650
Do you want to go?

15:05.840 --> 15:06.810
I bought so many things.

15:07.060 --> 15:07.750
It's a waste if we don't eat them.

15:08.290 --> 15:08.640
Go on in.

15:10.430 --> 15:11.650
If I don't go,

15:11.850 --> 15:13.080
shouldn't we explain it to her?

15:13.750 --> 15:14.420
I think

15:14.720 --> 15:15.690
she really wants you to go back.

15:16.330 --> 15:16.690
It's okay.

15:17.240 --> 15:18.150
I'll talk to her later.

15:20.060 --> 15:20.660
Chen.

15:20.810 --> 15:21.980
Someone is making trouble inside.

15:22.010 --> 15:23.360
I can't handle it.

15:24.720 --> 15:25.380
Wait here.

15:27.100 --> 15:27.770
Don't touch the bag.

15:28.080 --> 15:28.980
The water on it is dirty.

15:29.170 --> 15:29.610
It's not clean.

15:31.240 --> 15:32.270
You must give us an explanation.

15:33.140 --> 15:33.980
Calm down.

15:34.010 --> 15:34.810
Ask your boss to come out.

15:35.360 --> 15:36.070
Wait here.

15:36.100 --> 15:36.890
I'll go in and take a look.

15:40.170 --> 15:41.010
What are you looking at?

15:41.260 --> 15:41.940
Fix it!

15:43.700 --> 15:45.540
Why did you buy two big fish?

15:45.970 --> 15:47.250
Isn't there a small one too?

15:47.670 --> 15:48.600
Uncle Lu said

15:48.900 --> 15:49.950
he was scared you might want to eat a big fish

15:50.040 --> 15:50.560
and we didn't have one.

15:55.620 --> 15:56.020
Here.

16:03.860 --> 16:04.430
Sir.

16:07.920 --> 16:08.860
Can you

16:08.860 --> 16:09.900
get us some warm water?

16:10.450 --> 16:11.880
Okay. You go in first.

16:11.910 --> 16:13.100
I'll get you some water.

16:13.390 --> 16:14.140
Okay, thank you.

16:18.140 --> 16:19.020
Thank you.

16:19.900 --> 16:21.160
You're welcome.

16:21.180 --> 16:22.740
I'm happy that you came to chat with me.

16:22.770 --> 16:23.490
Come here more often.

16:24.440 --> 16:25.640
She will come often.

16:26.460 --> 16:27.230
I'll get going then.

16:27.280 --> 16:27.760
Go ahead.

16:29.930 --> 16:30.300
Wash your hands.

16:41.820 --> 16:42.730
Sister-in-law?

16:43.020 --> 16:43.560
Hai Dong?

16:43.600 --> 16:45.070
We've finally met.

16:45.700 --> 16:46.740
Meng Xiaoshan told me about you.

16:46.740 --> 16:47.540
Lu Chen told me about you.

16:47.540 --> 16:48.740
But I didn't get to see you.

16:48.900 --> 16:49.650
When did you get here?

16:49.910 --> 16:50.400
In the morning,

16:50.430 --> 16:50.940
around ten o’clock.

16:51.880 --> 16:53.260
Lu Chen didn't tell me. He's hiding you from me.

16:53.360 --> 16:53.980
If he'd told me,

16:53.980 --> 16:55.020
I'd have come immediately.

16:56.900 --> 16:57.380
Wait a minute.

16:57.530 --> 16:58.650
There are some punks outside

16:58.670 --> 16:59.230
causing trouble.

16:59.260 --> 16:59.900
I'll go take a look.

17:00.300 --> 17:01.350
I'll get rid of the water for you.

17:01.820 --> 17:02.180
Okay.

17:02.180 --> 17:03.210
Take this away too.

17:03.240 --> 17:03.550
Okay.

17:10.430 --> 17:11.260
You're not leaving tonight, right?

17:11.260 --> 17:11.819
Stay for dinner.

17:12.230 --> 17:12.680
I'm staying.

17:12.880 --> 17:13.890
I'll sleep at Meng Xiaoshan's place tonight.

17:14.319 --> 17:15.109
That's good.

17:22.819 --> 17:24.300
The fish jumped out just now.

17:24.319 --> 17:24.880
Qin Xiaonan and I got dirty

17:24.910 --> 17:26.390
when we put it back in.

17:28.220 --> 17:28.460
Let's go.

17:28.960 --> 17:29.520
Let's go cook.

17:33.060 --> 17:34.340
Is everything okay at the garage?

17:35.000 --> 17:35.420
It's nothing.

17:36.020 --> 17:36.770
Who do you think I am?

17:37.280 --> 17:38.430
I got nervous and forgot.

17:45.940 --> 17:46.250
Go

17:46.750 --> 17:47.410
and do your workbook.

18:07.700 --> 18:09.180
If we don't go,

18:09.180 --> 18:09.900
shouldn't we tell your mother

18:09.900 --> 18:10.980
in person?

18:11.900 --> 18:12.260
There's no need.

18:12.940 --> 18:13.700
I'll tell her myself.

18:15.340 --> 18:16.040
How do you want to eat it?

18:16.950 --> 18:17.790
What kind of fish is this?

18:18.340 --> 18:18.700
Mandarin fish.

18:21.380 --> 18:22.620
It's expensive.

18:24.660 --> 18:25.650
How expensive can a fish be?

18:27.700 --> 18:28.200
How do you want it?

18:30.870 --> 18:31.590
I want squirrel fish.

18:33.700 --> 18:35.070
You're still as picky as when you were young.

18:35.770 --> 18:36.490
Don't you think it's troublesome?

18:40.260 --> 18:40.730
Hai Dong.

18:41.090 --> 18:41.830
Let's eat together when you're free.

18:42.880 --> 18:43.520
Hai Dong.

18:43.840 --> 18:45.080
Business has been booming lately.

18:45.340 --> 18:46.220
Don't forget about us.

18:46.550 --> 18:47.440
Go away.

18:47.580 --> 18:48.230
Hurry up.

18:49.230 --> 18:50.270
Don't do anything stupid again.

18:50.820 --> 18:51.290
Hai Dong.

18:51.980 --> 18:53.100
Buy a packet of cornstarch for me!

18:54.470 --> 18:55.070
Okay.

19:05.170 --> 19:11.300
[Fortune Garden]

19:18.850 --> 19:20.210
What are you doing in front of my hotel?

19:20.310 --> 19:20.880
You want to borrow money?

19:21.860 --> 19:23.490
No, I'm buying cornstarch.

19:24.620 --> 19:26.130
Who can make you run errands for them?

19:26.500 --> 19:28.020
Chen. Who else could it be?

19:28.950 --> 19:29.670
He's cooking?

19:30.530 --> 19:31.100
Who is he hosting?

19:31.600 --> 19:32.600
Your sister, Gui Xiao.

19:34.950 --> 19:35.980
She's back?

19:36.840 --> 19:38.040
Tell her that

19:38.070 --> 19:38.990
I'll keep the door open for her tonight

19:39.010 --> 19:39.680
at my parents' place.

19:40.660 --> 19:40.990
Okay.

19:41.220 --> 19:42.020
I'll go in first.

19:42.050 --> 19:42.700
I'm so busy.

20:04.450 --> 20:04.780
Here.

20:05.890 --> 20:06.620
Check if it's too salty.

20:14.500 --> 20:15.020
It's not.

20:20.530 --> 20:21.210
It's really fresh.

20:32.980 --> 20:33.780
Come on.

20:57.580 --> 20:58.430
How did you do it?

20:58.570 --> 20:59.610
It opened just like that?

21:00.520 --> 21:00.950
Take it easy.

21:01.420 --> 21:02.020
Don't hurt yourself.

21:08.060 --> 21:08.750
I have a cousin

21:08.780 --> 21:09.830
who's in a SWAT team.

21:09.930 --> 21:10.610
She even trained to smash bricks

21:10.630 --> 21:11.440
with her bare hands.

21:11.890 --> 21:13.130
Do you know how to do it?

21:14.900 --> 21:15.380
I've never trained for it.

21:15.940 --> 21:16.720
I'm not good at that.

21:18.160 --> 21:18.810
But I once

21:18.840 --> 21:19.680
mentored a team member

21:19.700 --> 21:20.390
who liked to do it.

21:21.160 --> 21:22.250
He had a stack of them lined up.

21:23.220 --> 21:23.860
I think he must have smashed

21:23.860 --> 21:25.020
dozens of them in a row.

21:29.470 --> 21:30.110
That's great.

21:30.720 --> 21:31.160
Great.

21:33.620 --> 21:34.300
We were waiting for you.

21:34.900 --> 21:35.990
I've bought the stuff.

21:36.140 --> 21:36.890
I've also prepared

21:36.910 --> 21:37.810
alcohol and my sentimentality.

21:37.900 --> 21:38.680
We're just waiting for your dish.

21:38.710 --> 21:39.420
Let me have a good cry.

21:41.400 --> 21:42.000
I'll go cook.

21:55.660 --> 21:57.730
I saw his mother just now.

21:59.730 --> 22:00.910
Lu Chen’s mom came?

22:01.390 --> 22:02.940
It was most likely that aunt-in-law

22:02.970 --> 22:04.130
from the finance office who asked her to come.

22:04.800 --> 22:05.710
My mom told me that

22:06.370 --> 22:07.690
when Lu Chen was three,

22:08.490 --> 22:10.360
he was punished and scolded by his dad

22:10.660 --> 22:11.480
during Chinese New Year.

22:11.520 --> 22:12.230
It was just because Lu Chen

22:12.270 --> 22:13.130
had said something wrong.

22:13.980 --> 22:15.140
He stood beside the dining table

22:15.170 --> 22:16.050
for a whole night.

22:16.820 --> 22:18.230
Lu Chen’s mother wanted to see Lu Chen,

22:18.300 --> 22:19.520
but his aunt-in-law didn't let her.

22:20.690 --> 22:21.700
Lu Chen's father

22:21.700 --> 22:22.990
favored sons over daughters.

22:23.660 --> 22:25.310
He used to hit his sister whenever he got drunk.

22:25.510 --> 22:26.070
In the end,

22:26.230 --> 22:27.720
Lu Chen would deliberately provoke his father.

22:27.970 --> 22:29.060
He saved his sister many times.

22:30.490 --> 22:32.210
Now, he's finally grown up.

22:32.870 --> 22:33.410
It wasn't easy.

22:38.060 --> 22:38.510
By the way,

22:39.050 --> 22:40.720
are you two ready to make up?

22:42.660 --> 22:43.260
No.

22:44.180 --> 22:44.900
We're just friends.

22:47.340 --> 22:47.940
Just friends?

23:07.150 --> 23:08.660
Take care.

23:09.580 --> 23:10.830
I'll be happy

23:11.330 --> 23:12.130
if you two are happy.

23:28.760 --> 23:29.700
I've brought him back for you.

23:30.270 --> 23:31.070
Make him drink more water.

23:31.690 --> 23:32.460
Keep an eye on him tonight.

23:32.660 --> 23:33.190
Don't worry.

23:33.750 --> 23:34.410
Sister-in-law.

23:35.170 --> 23:35.870
Get in.

23:35.950 --> 23:36.900
Let's meet another day.

23:38.500 --> 23:38.940
Gui Xiao?

23:40.330 --> 23:41.050
I'm Hai Jianfeng.

23:41.070 --> 23:41.850
Do you remember me?

23:42.660 --> 23:43.220
Of course.

23:44.050 --> 23:44.980
Wait.

23:45.010 --> 23:46.180
I was in Dalian a couple of days ago,

23:46.300 --> 23:47.620
when they talked about having a class reunion.

23:47.620 --> 23:49.020
I thought it was a pity that I couldn't see you.

23:49.420 --> 23:50.100
You...

23:51.140 --> 23:51.780
Hai Jianfeng.

23:53.060 --> 23:54.640
You're not allowed to have designs on Gui Xiao anymore.

23:55.160 --> 23:57.200
She's Chen's wife now.

23:57.590 --> 23:59.140
What are you talking about?

23:59.380 --> 24:00.300
I was just excited

24:00.300 --> 24:01.060
to see an old classmate.

24:01.140 --> 24:01.690
Come on.

24:02.080 --> 24:02.810
Let me tell you.

24:03.440 --> 24:04.150
This brother of mine

24:05.120 --> 24:07.200
fell in love with your wife

24:07.230 --> 24:08.380
on the first day of secondary school.

24:09.540 --> 24:10.380
You wouldn't even believe it.

24:10.700 --> 24:11.910
Even now, he still has

24:11.940 --> 24:12.900
a photo of Gui Xiao

24:12.920 --> 24:13.820
by his bedside.

24:14.010 --> 24:15.820
It's been there since graduation!

24:18.160 --> 24:19.120
My brother is talking nonsense.

24:19.300 --> 24:20.370
G- Gui Xiao.

24:20.580 --> 24:22.060
You are Chen look good together.

24:22.100 --> 24:22.760
It wasn't easy for you two.

24:23.110 --> 24:23.800
Y- You look good together.

24:24.080 --> 24:25.580
Hasn't everyone had a crush?

24:26.400 --> 24:27.720
If Lu Chen hadn’t come back,

24:28.410 --> 24:29.640
you might have stood a chance.

24:30.220 --> 24:30.820
Brother, you...

24:30.850 --> 24:31.310
Alright.

24:31.340 --> 24:32.110
Let's stop talking.

24:35.820 --> 24:37.540
Why did you drink so much?

24:37.560 --> 24:37.850
Mom.

24:38.180 --> 24:39.390
Let me introduce them to you, Gui Xiao.

24:39.780 --> 24:40.620
This is my sister.

24:42.570 --> 24:43.240
This is my mom.

24:43.550 --> 24:44.620
We'll go in first.

24:45.150 --> 24:46.060
-Okay. -Go back.

24:48.160 --> 24:49.940
♫Easy come, easy go♫

24:50.220 --> 24:50.560
Alright.

24:52.420 --> 24:52.990
Where is the photo?

24:53.760 --> 24:54.340
Let me see.

24:55.370 --> 24:55.980
Chen.

24:56.210 --> 24:57.410
My brother is drunk.

24:57.430 --> 24:58.140
He was talking nonsense.

24:58.170 --> 24:59.010
I put it away a long time ago.

25:04.190 --> 25:05.100
I'll get it now.

25:05.130 --> 25:05.860
I'll get it for you now.

25:05.880 --> 25:06.680
W- Wait for me.

25:06.810 --> 25:07.340
There's no need!

25:36.960 --> 25:37.440
It's quite pretty.

25:42.050 --> 25:43.530
I don't even have this photo.

25:43.640 --> 25:44.720
Thank you for safekeeping it for me.

25:45.510 --> 25:46.030
You're welcome.

25:47.450 --> 25:48.570
We'll leave now.

25:49.140 --> 25:49.660
Go back in.

26:11.150 --> 26:12.250
I was so young back then.

26:17.040 --> 26:18.160
How did he get your photo?

26:19.660 --> 26:20.370
I don't know.

26:21.160 --> 26:22.220
I remember the teacher

26:22.220 --> 26:23.180
taking this photo.

26:23.910 --> 26:25.080
Maybe he asked the teacher for it.

26:36.280 --> 26:37.050
He's quite thoughtful.

27:31.130 --> 27:32.140
If you hadn't come to Qining,

27:33.830 --> 27:34.910
I wouldn't have come back.

27:37.610 --> 27:38.720
The last time I went to Qining,

27:40.580 --> 27:41.740
