27:52.740 --> 27:54.140
I can even recite it backwards.

27:59.950 --> 28:00.750
Recite it for me.

28:04.180 --> 28:05.060
I've forgotten now.

28:07.620 --> 28:08.460
You forgot it once you saw me?

28:22.790 --> 28:23.650
Call me before going to bed.

28:31.140 --> 28:31.540
Bye.

29:16.260 --> 29:17.890
I was worried that you'll sleep at the garage.

29:17.930 --> 29:18.800
There are too many prying eyes there.

29:20.180 --> 29:21.000
Come to think of it,

29:21.100 --> 29:22.140
Lu Chen is quite sensible.

29:22.630 --> 29:23.640
He really sent you here.

29:32.750 --> 29:34.180
It's no different from when you dated

29:34.180 --> 29:35.100
when you were young.

29:35.930 --> 29:37.140
You still can't bear to part with him.

29:37.620 --> 29:38.450
It's like you earn money

29:38.480 --> 29:39.650
by taking one more look at him.

29:41.810 --> 29:43.000
My parents are not home today.

29:43.100 --> 29:43.710
It's just the two of us.

29:57.310 --> 29:58.620
I saw his mother today.

30:00.120 --> 30:01.800
She doesn’t look like Lu Chen at all.

30:03.040 --> 30:03.880
I didn’t recognize her.

30:05.640 --> 30:07.490
His parents are hard to get along with.

30:07.810 --> 30:08.690
I can't be bothered to deal with them

30:08.710 --> 30:09.610
even though I'm so sociable.

30:10.130 --> 30:10.730
You

30:11.250 --> 30:12.390
better not see them often.

30:15.360 --> 30:17.070
Did you talk to him

30:17.120 --> 30:17.760
after sending Hai Dong back?

30:19.820 --> 30:20.270
No.

30:21.960 --> 30:23.370
You've cleared all the obstacles.

30:23.390 --> 30:25.050
Hurry up if you want to do something about it.

30:29.710 --> 30:30.670
I'll take my time.

