♫We need to cultivate our relationship♫

33:03.120 --> 33:05.780
♫I believe you can do it♫

33:05.930 --> 33:06.730
Yes.

33:08.170 --> 33:09.410
Aren't you afraid of being seen?

33:18.750 --> 33:20.030
What's wrong? Did you fall?

33:21.030 --> 33:21.570
Someone is coming.

33:22.050 --> 33:22.550
I'm leaving.

33:36.170 --> 33:36.710
Sleep early.

34:18.840 --> 34:19.800
Uncle Lu.

34:20.250 --> 34:21.630
I thought you weren't coming back

34:21.650 --> 34:22.889
to sleep tonight.

34:23.659 --> 34:24.449
Where else could  go?

34:27.139 --> 34:27.960
Have you gotten used to it here?

34:33.699 --> 34:34.380
Do you miss home?

34:36.960 --> 34:38.880
I've been here for so long.

34:39.719 --> 34:41.260
Why did you only ask me tonight?

34:51.060 --> 34:51.770
Aunt Gui Xiao...

34:54.699 --> 34:55.219
Uncle.

34:55.670 --> 34:56.380
What do you want to ask?

34:57.650 --> 34:58.100
Go to sleep.

35:07.290 --> 35:07.820
What has Aunt Gui Xiao

35:07.820 --> 35:08.570
been doing recently?

35:12.260 --> 35:12.970
I didn't have time to ask.

35:13.700 --> 35:14.760
Do you know about her job?

35:19.900 --> 35:22.900
Is there anything wrong with her work?

35:23.700 --> 35:26.150
Is it against the rules?

35:26.180 --> 35:26.750
No.

35:27.780 --> 35:28.860
I just want to know.

35:31.870 --> 35:33.350
Just ask Aunt Gui Xiao.

35:37.930 --> 35:39.030
It's 2 a.m.

35:39.270 --> 35:39.790
How do I ask?

35:42.030 --> 35:43.600
Ask her tomorrow.

35:49.220 --> 35:50.200
I'm not sure.

35:52.900 --> 35:55.730
I think she's an investor.

35:57.380 --> 35:59.960
She has money and looks for projects everywhere.

36:00.780 --> 36:05.180
She told her colleagues she was investing in...

36:05.730 --> 36:07.600
in educational...

36:08.980 --> 36:10.290
educational...

36:11.970 --> 36:12.890
new energy?

36:14.180 --> 36:15.180
I think so.

36:15.630 --> 36:15.980
Go to sleep.

36:18.770 --> 36:19.170
Your hand.

36:34.400 --> 36:35.400
Get up.

36:35.640 --> 36:36.390
You're going to be late.

36:37.400 --> 36:38.480
Stop it.

36:38.580 --> 36:39.420
I’m sleepy.

36:42.820 --> 36:44.020
Lu Chen is here

36:44.020 --> 36:45.270
to pick you up to go to school.

36:52.400 --> 36:52.950
I want...

36:53.490 --> 36:55.500
My flight is at twelve.

36:55.610 --> 36:56.980
Let me sleep until eight.

36:58.180 --> 36:59.220
Why would I lie to you?

36:59.220 --> 37:00.710
Lu Chen brought breakfast.

37:26.760 --> 37:27.020
Morning.

37:29.640 --> 37:30.190
I bought it for you.

37:37.780 --> 37:38.580
The auntie outside the school gate

37:38.620 --> 37:39.580
opened her own store.

37:40.260 --> 37:40.750
It tastes the same.

37:46.410 --> 37:47.470
It's still hot.

37:49.540 --> 37:50.260
Have you eaten?

37:51.180 --> 37:52.350
I ate at the garage.

37:52.880 --> 37:53.680
I didn't have time to eat on the way.

38:00.270 --> 38:01.260
I'm going back to work soon.

38:02.020 --> 38:02.590
There's a secret mission.

38:03.390 --> 38:05.190
I won't be able to use my phone for a while.

38:10.590 --> 38:12.110
The nature of my work is a bit different.

38:12.520 --> 38:13.530
I become uncontactable at times

38:14.840 --> 38:15.820
and cannot explain anything.

38:16.510 --> 38:17.600
I'm telling you in advance

38:17.990 --> 38:18.820
so you don't overthink this.

38:27.400 --> 38:27.730
Well...

38:28.680 --> 38:29.280
I'll be off now.

38:38.110 --> 38:38.620
You're still here?

38:42.530 --> 38:43.380
It was so busy

38:43.910 --> 38:44.680
this time.

38:45.440 --> 38:46.320
Let's talk properly

38:47.580 --> 38:48.260
when you come back from your business trip.

38:49.780 --> 38:50.270
About what?

38:54.750 --> 38:55.450
Your job.

38:55.980 --> 38:56.660
My job.

38:57.280 --> 38:58.480
My family background.

38:59.220 --> 38:59.830
The situation

38:59.860 --> 39:00.620
after my transfer back.

39:01.500 --> 39:02.180
My salary

39:02.850 --> 39:03.900
and my personal assets.

39:05.420 --> 39:06.410
When we were in school,

39:06.630 --> 39:07.810
I didn't tell you much about these.

39:08.410 --> 39:10.470
I want to make them clear this time.

39:15.330 --> 39:16.200
You're thoughtful.

39:16.540 --> 39:17.290
You should make them clear.

39:22.220 --> 39:22.830
Of course,

39:22.850 --> 39:23.620
if you

39:23.650 --> 39:24.650
just want to date,

39:24.680 --> 39:25.290
then it's not necessary.

39:25.320 --> 39:25.850
There's no need to say.

39:26.440 --> 39:27.550
It's good to retain

39:27.580 --> 39:28.480
a bit of the mystery.

39:28.690 --> 39:29.530
Go to work.

39:29.740 --> 39:30.640
I'm going too after I eat.

39:31.990 --> 39:32.290
Okay.

39:33.410 --> 39:34.060
We'll talk about it later.

39:38.980 --> 39:39.580
I’m leaving.

39:53.850 --> 39:55.130
Does your dad know Lu Chen is back?

39:57.260 --> 39:57.970
I don’t want to tell him.

40:06.150 --> 40:10.420
[Hongrun Chenghua]

40:12.370 --> 40:12.750
I thought

40:12.780 --> 40:14.090
you would wait for me at the airport.

40:14.820 --> 40:16.070
I saw that I still had some time,

40:16.420 --> 40:17.700
so I came back to attend the weekly meeting.

40:21.200 --> 40:22.750
You two. Tell me

40:22.780 --> 40:23.860
about your recent projects.

40:29.360 --> 40:30.330
Pass me the agenda.

40:34.130 --> 40:34.660
You go first.

40:34.880 --> 40:35.920
I'll tell you one by one.

40:35.990 --> 40:36.310
Okay.

40:36.710 --> 40:38.190
They insist that the shareholders

40:38.220 --> 40:39.540
should have veto rights.

40:39.800 --> 40:40.550
I told them

40:40.590 --> 40:41.590
I can't promise them something like that,

40:41.800 --> 40:42.840
and that the bosses on both sides

40:42.860 --> 40:43.510
need to discuss this directly.

40:44.210 --> 40:44.980
Make an appointment

40:44.980 --> 40:46.240
for a teleconference with Mr. Wu.

40:47.290 --> 40:48.210
After the secretary confirms it,

40:48.230 --> 40:49.250
email the other party

40:49.510 --> 40:50.590
and CC Mr. Wu and me.

40:54.880 --> 40:56.210
Also, they think

40:56.240 --> 40:57.920
the minimum of 13% of shares

40:57.940 --> 40:58.470
is too low.

40:58.500 --> 40:59.850
They're requesting a directly proportionate capital increase.

41:02.800 --> 41:03.330
We have been dealing with this

41:03.350 --> 41:05.020
for two weeks.

41:08.550 --> 41:09.110
How about this?

41:09.300 --> 41:10.270
Delete the clause on the contract

41:10.290 --> 41:11.390
that precludes capital increase

41:11.570 --> 41:12.600
and proceed with the negotiations.

41:12.940 --> 41:13.260
Okay.

41:14.540 --> 41:15.740
The bottom line I'm giving you

41:16.460 --> 41:17.660
is that we can add a clause for capital increase

41:17.680 --> 41:18.860
into the contract,

41:19.450 --> 41:20.930
but it cannot stipulate any specific requirements.

41:22.490 --> 41:23.880
For instance, terms like

41:24.300 --> 41:25.580
"directly proportionate"

41:25.600 --> 41:26.670
must not appear in the contract.

41:28.450 --> 41:28.940
Remember.

41:29.850 --> 41:30.330
We can only

41:30.360 --> 41:32.330
reveal our bottom line

41:32.490 --> 41:33.430
after at least three rounds of negotiation.

41:34.190 --> 41:34.500
Okay.

41:35.940 --> 41:36.670
Let me teach you.

41:37.610 --> 41:39.220
Every time the negotiations reach a stalemate,

41:39.580 --> 41:40.350
just say,

41:41.050 --> 41:42.310
"I can't make this decision.

41:42.740 --> 41:43.700
Let me ask my boss."

41:44.580 --> 41:46.910
Then, answer them the next day.

41:48.030 --> 41:50.180
If that doesn't work, tell them,

41:51.740 --> 41:53.620
"My boss is very unaccommodating.

41:53.620 --> 41:55.010
She's very difficult to talk to.

41:55.130 --> 41:56.970
I'll try to persuade her again."

41:57.750 --> 41:58.310
Yes.

41:58.330 --> 41:59.170
Blame it all on me.

41:59.710 --> 42:00.350
I am here

42:00.410 --> 42:01.540
to act as your shield.

42:02.690 --> 42:03.180
Don't worry.

42:03.440 --> 42:04.620
I won't take it to heart

42:04.690 --> 42:05.940
no matter how many bad things you say about me.

42:20.040 --> 42:20.440
Dad.

42:23.270 --> 42:23.960
I'm at the airport.

42:38.700 --> 42:39.570
My dad is here.
